Question: Is the old man to the left or to the right of the chair that is to the left of the cups?

Reference Answer: The man is to the left of the chair.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n518912.jpg

Program:

```
 Is A <planar pos> or <planar pos> B?
Program:
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='cups')
IMAGE0=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='chair')
IMAGE1=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='old man')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX2)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'left' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'right'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
